<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Login to Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #cacaca;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #e8e8e8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .logo-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #000000;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #3e3e3e;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #447aee;
      color: #e8e8e8;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #004a98;
    }
    .code-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .code {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #cacaca;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      color: #000000;
    }
    .divider {
      text-align: center;
      color: #6e6e6e;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>Hey {{userName}}!</p>
    {{#if loginCode}}
    <p>To log in on the device you started from, enter this code in the app:</p>
    <div class="code-container">
      <span class="code">{{loginCode}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="divider">— or —</div>
    {{/if}}
    <p>Click the button below to log in with a magic link:</p>
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="{{magicLink}}" class="button">Login</a>
    </div>
    <p>This code and link expire in {{linkExpiresIn}} minutes.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this login, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Vantik Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>